title: BONUS: Antonio Brown is Released (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
The Patriots released Antonio Brown. Is he worth rostering in a redraft league? How about a keeper league? And now what is the value of the rest of the Pats? Brady, Edelman, Gordon, Dorsett, Michel, White and Burkhead are all discussed.
